description: iCarez is a young brand specializing in high-end screen protector, originally designed in Seattle, USA. With prefect cutting reaching 0.1mm accuracy, iCarez is the brand can meet up with Apple standard so far. Made of a new generation of Grade A, ECO materials in high purity with Japanese latest Nano coating technology,our products don't contain any glue and heavy metals. No harsh to human skin, it makes you and your families ease to use.
title: iCarez® [HD Clear] Highest Quality Premium Screen Protector for Apple iPad Mini / iPad Mini 2 High Definition Ultra Clear Anti Bacterial Anti-Oil Anti Scratch Bubble free Reduce Fingerprint No rainbow washable Screen Protector **PET Film Made in Japan** Easy install & Green healthy Product with Lifetime Replacement Warranty (2-Pack) - Retail Packaging 2014
